	<div id='headerban'  class='avia-section av-47wkh7s-3a5208c0cf8f9d37a1ca7919bc0309cb main_color avia-section-large avia-no-border-styling  avia-builder-el-0  el_before_av_section  avia-builder-el-first  avia-full-stretch avia-bg-style-scroll av-minimum-height av-minimum-height-custom av-height-custom  container_wrap fullsize'  data-section-bg-repeat='stretch' data-av_minimum_height_px='350'><div class='container av-section-cont-open' style='height:350px'><main  role="main" itemprop="mainContentOfPage"  class='template-page content  av-content-full alpha units'><div class='post-entry post-entry-type-page post-entry-5720'><div class='entry-content-wrapper clearfix'>
<div class='flex_column_table av-45s3zpk-0218381e88d82786775fe5f00c368bf5 sc-av_one_full av-equal-height-column-flextable'><div  class='flex_column av-45s3zpk-0218381e88d82786775fe5f00c368bf5 av_one_full  avia-builder-el-1  avia-builder-el-no-sibling  first flex_column_table_cell av-equal-height-column av-align-middle av-zero-column-padding  '     ><section  class='av_textblock_section av-43n9cy0-917d861ab094345ebc8324afff45a8bd '   itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock av_inherit_color'  itemprop="text" ><h1 style="font-weight: 800; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 38px; color: white!important; text-transform: initial;">Create Better Digital Transformation Outcomes with NVT Phybridge Power over Ethernet (PoE) Switches &#038; Network Innovations</h1>
<p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 29px; font-weight: 300; text-align: center; max-width: 1000px; margin: auto; padding-top: 4px;color:white;">Organizations applying traditional local area network design to enable IP devices have experienced higher costs, greater network complexity, and cyber-security concerns. NVT Phybridge long-reach Power over Ethernet switches and networking solutions help businesses improve digital transformation outcomes with a simple, secure, and cost-effective way to connect IP endpoints. Join the thousands of satisfied customers who have successfully modernized to the next generation of intelligent devices to ensure business success today and into the future!</p>
<p style="font-weight: 800;font-size: 19px; line-height: 29px; text-align: center; max-width: 1000px; margin: auto; padding-top: 4px;color:white; ">All NVT Phybridge IP products are made in North America and are TAA and NDAA compliant.</p>
</div></section>
<section class="avia_codeblock_section  avia_code_block_0"  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_codeblock '  itemprop="text" ><style>
