<section  class='av_textblock_section av-9mt4ag-419a0fdd41e3c3910e92b8cfee6c5c15 '   itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock av_inherit_color'  itemprop="text" ><p style="text-align: left; font-weight: 100;">We’ve helped thousands of partners Avoid The Trap, generating over $1 billion in revenue with stronger margins. Now, the Trap Avoided Promotion is here to help you replicate the success by overcoming the reach and cable type limitations of standard switches with NVT Phybridge PoE innovations. Help your customers achieve better ROI while you accelerate timelines, reduce complexity, and outpace the competition.</p>
</div></section>
