</svg><span class='avia_hidden_link_text'>Next</span></a></div><div class='avia-slideshow-dots avia-slideshow-controls'><a href='#1' class='goto-slide active' >1</a><a href='#2' class='goto-slide ' >2</a><a href='#3' class='goto-slide ' >3</a><a href='#4' class='goto-slide ' >4</a><a href='#5' class='goto-slide ' >5</a></div></div><div class="avia-content-slider-inner"><div class="slide-entry-wrap"><section class='slide-entry av-2u60laz-e9ed52961c1f9cbe6873a16f9c1d6d16 flex_column av_fullwidth post-entry slide-entry-overview slide-loop-1 slide-parity-odd  first'  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='slide-entry-excerpt entry-content'  itemprop="text" ><p style="text-align: center; color: #3492d1; font-size: 18px; line-height: 22px; font-weight: 800;">“NVT Phybridge PoE switches allowed us to create a robust and secure network backbone for our new IP Intercom System. We now have greater communication flexibility to help our operators improve the response time to customer needs.”</p>
<p style="text-align: center; color: #3492d1; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 800;"><span style="font-weight: 100;">Jeff Thurston &#8211; Project Manager, Toronto Transit Commission (TTC)<br />
</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center; color: #3492d1; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 100;"><a class="quotebtn" href="https://www.nvtphybridge.com/toronto-transit-commission/">Read the full story</a></p>
</div></section></div><div class="slide-entry-wrap"><section class='slide-entry av-2pvmw57-abd60aa9914d67de8a5cb527203cbcda flex_column av_fullwidth post-entry slide-entry-overview slide-loop-2 slide-parity-odd  first'  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='slide-entry-excerpt entry-content'  itemprop="text" ><p style="text-align: center; color: #3492d1; font-size: 18px; line-height: 22px; font-weight: 800;">“Installing the NVT Phybridge PoE switches was smooth and straightforward. Their technology allowed us to modernize our schools without having to deal with construction. We did our homework. Re-using our existing cabling and turning it into a more secure transmission model was a huge win for us and a huge win for our taxpayers. This really was a win for everyone.”</p>
<p style="text-align: center; color: #3492d1; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 800;"><span style="font-weight: 100;">David Spann &#8211; CIO, McKinney Independent School District</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center; color: #3492d1; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 100;"><a class="quotebtn" href="https://www.nvtphybridge.com/mckinney-isd/">Read the full story</a></p>
</div></section></div><div class="slide-entry-wrap"><section class='slide-entry av-1w7rtiz-32b6c3b2b4a33fb074c312f570637af1 flex_column av_fullwidth post-entry slide-entry-overview slide-loop-3 slide-parity-odd  first'  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='slide-entry-excerpt entry-content'  itemprop="text" ><p style="text-align: center; color: #3492d1; font-size: 18px; line-height: 22px; font-weight: 800;">“NVT Phybridge Power over Ethernet switches allowed us to meet strict Historic Preservation requirements and quickly deploy IP cameras without re-cabling. It is incredible that we can support 4K ultra-high-definition IP cameras using the existing category-3 cable. NVT Phybridge helped prevent seven difficult cable runs and the disruption that comes with pulling cable. I am thrilled to have avoided the rip-and-replace of existing cabling while not compromising on performance.”</p>
<p style="text-align: center; color: #3492d1; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 800;"><span style="font-weight: 100;">Rev. Dr. Manoj Mathew Zacharia &#8211; Rector, St. Anne’s Parish</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center; color: #3492d1; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 100;"><a class="quotebtn" href="https://www.nvtphybridge.com/st-annes-church/">Read the full story</a></p>
</div></section></div><div class="slide-entry-wrap"><section class='slide-entry av-1jsna7v-52bb71e73cda007c0685a18f1aaf6c6b flex_column av_fullwidth post-entry slide-entry-overview slide-loop-4 slide-parity-odd  first'  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='slide-entry-excerpt entry-content'  itemprop="text" ><p style="text-align: center; color: #3492d1; font-size: 18px; line-height: 22px; font-weight: 800;">“We have used NVT Phybridge PoE switches many times and have found them to be extremely flexible, dynamic, and practical. Once again, we exceeded the customer’s expectations using NVT Phybridge technology and have experienced no issues.”</p>
<p style="text-align: center; color: #3492d1; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 800;"><span style="font-weight: 100;">Eduardo Rodriguez Vanegas General Manager, Telenet</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center; color: #3492d1; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 100;"><a class="quotebtn" href="https://www.nvtphybridge.com/punto-sur-2/">Read the full story</a></p>
</div></section></div><div class="slide-entry-wrap"><section class='slide-entry av-11tj8t7-f2fe551f2855df69fbd4ddcf21f8e337 flex_column av_fullwidth post-entry slide-entry-overview slide-loop-5 slide-parity-odd  post-entry-last  first'  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='slide-entry-excerpt entry-content'  itemprop="text" ><p style="text-align: center; color: #3492d1; font-size: 18px; line-height: 22px; font-weight: 800;">“The client was very satisfied as they were able to avoid costly trenching and unsightly conduit runs to install the new IP cameras. We are confident that this project would not have been possible without NVT Phybridge PoE switches.”</p>
<p style="text-align: center; color: #3492d1; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 800;"><span style="font-weight: 100;">Behzad Faridnia &#8211; Founder and Chief Innovator, OC Tech Innovations</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center; color: #3492d1; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 100;"><a class="quotebtn" href="https://www.nvtphybridge.com/el-paseo-south-gate/">Read the full story</a></p>
</div></section></div></div></div>
